&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own end-to-end inference optimization across our model stack — LLMs, audio models, and diffusion-based components&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement and tune KV cache strategies for long-context conversations, including eviction policies, compression, and memory-efficient attention&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evaluate, deploy, and extend inference serving frameworks (vLLM, SGLang, TensorRT-LLM, etc.) for our specific workloads&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Profile and benchmark end-to-end latency and throughput; identify and systematically eliminate bottlenecks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build internal tooling that makes optimization work faster and more rigorous — profiling viewers, end-to-end inference test harnesses, and other infrastructure that helps the team move quickly&lt;/li&gt;
